description:
John Fetterman once pulled a gun on a black man going for a jog. The Biden Regime is changing Title IX to make "gender identity" a protected class. Former Trump WH staffer Karoline Leavitt, running for Congress in New Hampshire joins C&B to tell us why she's fighting to become the first Gen-Z member of Congress. GOP has a bunch of young conservation all-stars running for office.
